### Forgot password - request OTP
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "your-user-email@example.com"
}

### Verify reset OTP
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/verify-reset-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "your-user-email@example.com",
	"otp": "123456"
}

### Reset password
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "your-user-email@example.com",
	"resetToken": "PASTE_RESET_TOKEN_FROM_VERIFY_RESPONSE",
	"password": "NewStrongPassword@123",
	"confirmPassword": "NewStrongPassword@123"
}

### Event reminders - run scheduled window manually (admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/event-reminders/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"userId": "PASTE_ADMIN_USER_ID"
}

### Event reminders - force mode (admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/event-reminders/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"userId": "PASTE_ADMIN_USER_ID",
	"force": true
}
